SimpleParser - Class in com.slickpath.mobile.android.simple.vm.parser
Parses file for commands, parameters, variables and symbols Possible line combinations COMMAND COMMAND PARAMETER COMMAND VAR COMMAND SYMBOL SYMBOL COMMENT Definitions: COMMAND - string PARAMETER - string (typically an integer, but can be VAR OR SYMBOL) VAR - string starting with 'g' - Variable memory location reference SYMBOL - [string] - note if a SYMBOL is used in a parameter it is a reference to an existing SYMBOL, that SYMBOL represents the line it is defined on.
